Syntax:

if (condition) {

}


example:

if(hour < 18){
    greeting = "Good day;
}


The else statement

if(condition){

}else{

}

example:
if(hour < 18){
    greeting = "Good day";
} else {
    greeting = "Good evening";
}




3.The else if statement

if(condition) {

}else if(condition)

{else}

}

example:

if(time < 10){
    greeting = "Good morning";
} else if(time < 20){
    greeting = "Good day";
} else {
    greeting = "Good evening"
}

// switch statement

syntax:

 4. switch(expression){
    case x:

    break;

    case y:

    break;

    default:
}

example:

switch (new Date().getDay()){
    case O:
    day = "Sunday";
    break;

    case 1:
    day = "Monday";
    break;

    case 6:
    day = "Saturday";
}